      "date": "2019-11-13 05:55:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI'm guessing to some extent, but it seem likely that upstream Linux patch\n\nCommit 86ff7c2a80cd (\"blk-mq: introduce BLK_STS_DEV_RESOURCE\")\n\nin Linux 4.16 addresses the same underlying problem, though the details are all different.\nIt might be worth looking over that patch and confirming that it is the same idea, and looking to see if there might be something else in there that we need.",
